of this game and therefore solo a lot.<br>
I urge you all to post on the Sony EQ Developers board, your feelings about this, and maybe we can get them to up the stats on these items so it is more level with the time/effort taken to get them.<br>
I for 1 have been chasing 1 item for almost 3 months now, and I am gonna just buy the better BP I saw as the stats are better, but I would still like to finish these quests as they are fun.<br>
<br>
Just my 2 CP worth,<br>
